email
  Last email used for logging in.
  Usually set with radio login.

session_key
  Used for authentication.
  Usually set with radio login.

listen_key
  Used for generating playlists.
  Usually set with radio login.

network
  Specify the AudioAddict network you are currently listening to.
  Usually set with radio set.

channel
  Specify the AudioAddict channel you are currently listening to.
  Usually set with radio set.

like_log
  Specify the path to store all your positive votes.
  If this is not set, votes will only be sent to AudioAddict and not logged
  locally.

cache_dir
  Specify the path to store API response cache.
  Default: ~/.audio_addict/cache

cache_life
  Specify the cache life period.
  Default: 6h.

